      <abstract id="aspace_2078b6b542102de5eef410b643edc7f5">Collection is a set of postcards
        (including photograph postcards) from late 19th and 20th century Turkey, depicting scenes
        and people in İzmir (Smyrna), Turkey. Materials have been individually numbered and
        described in English, French, and Turkish.</abstract>
